thiran]] production ''[[Vil Ambu]]''.<ref>http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/tamil/Packing-Punches-in-Acchamindri/2015/04/06article2749237.ece</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+Key\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Language !! Notes\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Kadhalagi]]'' || Nandhini Velu Nachiyar || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Yuddham Sei]]'' || Suja || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[April Fool (2014 film)|April Fool]]'' || Satya || Telugu ||\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Megha (2014 film)|Megha]]'' || Meghavathy || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Darling (2015 Tamil film)|Darling]]'' || Swati || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''Oru Nodiyil'' || Savi  || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Enakkul Oruvan (2015 film)|Enakkul Oruvan]]'' || || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Puriyadha Anandam Puthithaga Arambam]]'' || Nila || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Kaththukkutti]]'' || Bhuvana || Tamil || [[Edison Awards (India)|Edison Award for Best Actress in a Social Awareness Movie]] \n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Vil Ambu]]'' || Nithya || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Navarasa Thilagam]]''  || Chithra || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2016 ||  ''[[Jithan 2]]''|| Priya (the sprit girl)  || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2016 ||  ''[[Dharma Durai (2016 film)|Dharma Durai]]'' || Stella || Tamil || \n|-\n| 2016 ||  ''[[Achamindri]]'' || Malarvizhi || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[Mupparimanam]]'' || Anusha || Tamil ||     \n|- \n| 2017  || ''[[1971: Beyond Borders]]''  || || Malayalam || \n|-\n| 2017 || ''[[Saravanan Irukka Bayamaen]]'' || Fathima || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2017  || ''Oy Ninne''|| Vedha || Telugu ||\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Kaala Koothu]]'' || Revathi || Tamil ||                  \n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Sathru (2019 film)|Sathru]]'' || Darshini || Tamil || \n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Pottu (film)|Pottu]]'' || Nithya || Tamil || \n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[Rajavukku Check]]'' ||Aathira