er\" | '''2'''\n| [[Ren\u00e9e Roca]] / [[Donald Adair]]\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Susan Wynne]] / [[Joseph Druar]]\n|- bgcolor=\"#d1c571\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''4'''\n| [[April Sargent]] / [[Russ Witherby]]\n|-\n!5\n|Ann Hensel / James Yorke\n|}\n\n==Junior-level results==\n===Men===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n! CF\n! SP\n! FS\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Todd Eldredge]] ||||6||2\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Patrick Brault]] ||||1||1\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Craig Heath]] ||||||\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|-\n! 5\n| [[Shepherd Clark]]\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|-\n! 11\n| [[Aren Nielsen]]\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|}\n\n===Ladies===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Jeri Campbell]]\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Kristi Yamaguchi]]\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Tonia Kwiatkowski]]\n|- bgcolor=\"#d1c571\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''4'''\n| [[Nancy Kerrigan]]\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|}\n\n===Pairs===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Kellie Creel]] / [[David McGovern]]\n|- bgcolor=\"silver\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Michelle Laughlin]] / [[Mark Naylor (figure skater)|Mark Naylor]]\n|- bgcolor=\"cc9966\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''3'''\n| [[Julianne Thompson]] / [[Brian Geddeis]]\n|- bgcolor=\"#d1c571\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''4'''\n| [[Sara Powell]] / [[Robert Powell (figure skater)|Robert Powell]]\n|-\n! 5\n| [[Lara Dunlap]] / [[John Denton (figure skater)|John Denton]]\n|-\n! 6\n| [[Wendy Weston]] / [[David Goodman (figure skater)|David Goodman]]\n|-\n! 7\n| [[Paula Visingardi]] / [[Jeffrey Meyers (figure skater)|Jeffrey Meyers]]\n|-\n! ...\n| \n|}\n\n===Ice dancing===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Jennifer Benz]] / [[Jeffrey Benz]]\n|}\n\n==Novice-level results==\n===Men===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[John Baldwin (figure skater)|John Baldwin Jr.]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Damon Allen (figure skater)|Damon Allen]]\n|}\n\n===Ladies===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Rank\n! Name\n|- bgcolor=\"gold\"\n| align=\"center\" | '''1'''\n| [[Amy Holmberg]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | '''2'''\n| [[Berkley Villard]]\n|}\n\n===Pairs===\n\n===Ice dancing===\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=NT150530>{{cite news |url= http://www.thenewstribune.com/news/local/article26295622.html |title= What\u2019s the biggest sporting event in South Sound history? |first= Craig |last= Hill |work= The News Tribune |date= May 30, 2015 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20171016174013/http://www.thenewstribune.com/news/local/article26295622.html |archivedate= October 16, 2017 |url-status= live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=WP870208>{{cite news |url= https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/sports/1987/02/09/boitano-confident-after-3rd-us-skating-title/7d749068-9cc9-486d-8708-65a1b9417e39/ |title= Boitano confident after 3rd U.S. skating title |work= [[Washington Post]] |date= February 8, 1987 }}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.resultscorner.com/Event.aspx?EventID=999 ladies' results]{{Dead link|date=February 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20071011105350/http://www.pairsonice.net/compview.php?c=19880104 pairs' results]\n\n{{US Nationals Figure skating}}\n\n[[Category:U.S. Figure Skating Championships]]\n[[Category:1987 in figure skating|United States Figure Skating Championships, 1987]]\n[[Category:1987 in American sports|United States Figure Skating Championships, 1987]]\n[[Category:January 1987 sports events in the United States]]\n", "text_old": "{{more citations needed|date=March 2014}}\n{{Infobox Figure Skating Competition\n| title = 1